full_text: I wish it were acceptable to scream in public the way Amanda Seyfried (as Elizabeth Holmes, ofc) did in #TheDropout finale …

So … I may have been flipping through #ShipwreckGirl before I actually start reading it, but … I couldn’t be happier to have my TKOS homies back.  You know, eventually 😉 I always like it when authors tie in stuff from their other books
